    "en": {
      "title": "Gold jewelery robbery by throwing chilli powder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An incident was reported in Great Weston-Scalpa Estate where a woman was thrown chilli powder in her face and robbed of a 2.5lb gold chain from her neck.",
        "While the woman was working in the kitchen behind her house, an unidentified man threw chilli powder on her face, gagged her and stole a 2.5-pound gold chain from her neck and fled.",
        "After this, when the woman screamed, the neighbors also ran and searched for the thief, but he escaped from there.",
        "In connection with this incident, the Thalawakkalai police are involved in searching for the suspect. (R)"
      ],
